(20, 4, 'Admission Requirements', 'Mahitaji ya Kujiunga na Chuo', '<p>Thank you for your interest in the college of Information and Communication Technologies (CoICT) at the University of Dar es Salaam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Choosing a university is no small feat. It&#39;s important to make sure that the schools you apply to have the programs and resources that meet your personal and academic needs. It&#39;s also important to understand what the college or schools expect from you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe the College of Information and Communication Technologies (CoICT) of the University of Dar es Salaam (UDSM) offers some of the best academic and student-services programs around; our undergraduates and postgraduates are some of the most accomplished and motivated students anywhere. Find out for yourself. Use the links below to learn more about what it takes to be CoICT student</p>\r\n', '<p>Asante kwa kuonyesha nia ya kujiunga na chuo cha Teknolojia ya Taarifa na Mawasiliano (CoICT) katika Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uchaguzi wa chuo kikuu sio mdogo sana. Ni muhimu kuhakikisha kwamba shule unayotaka kuwa na mipango na rasilimali zinazofikia mahitaji yako binafsi na ya kitaaluma. Ni muhimu pia kuelewa nini chuo au shule zinatarajia kutoka kwako.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tunaamini Chuo cha Teknolojia ya Habari na Mawasiliano (CoICT) ya Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam (UDSM) inatoa baadhi ya mipango bora zaidi ya kitaaluma na ya wanafunzi karibu; wanafunzi wetu wa kwanza na wahitimu wao ni baadhi ya wanafunzi wengi waliofikia na wenye motisha popote. Jifunze mwenyewe. Tumia viungo chini ili ujifunze zaidi kuhusu kile kinachohitajika kuwa mwanafunzi wa COT</p>\r\n', 'UNIT4_Admission Requirements.pdf', '2017-11-10 14:04:02', '2017-11-30 15:46:25', 1, 0, '/colleges/coict/announcements/admission-requirements'),
(21, 11, 'tests announcement', 'tests announcement', '<p>tests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcement</p>\r\n', '<p>tests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcementtests announcement</p>\r\n', NULL, '2017-11-11 11:30:22', NULL, 2, 0, '/colleges/cohu/announcements/tests-announcement'),
(22, 11, 'invitation to join german course', 'invitation to join german course', '<p><strong>English is a Must, but German is a Plus</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nBroaden your linguistic horizon and choose German as a valuable asset for your future<br />\r\nby joining the German Language Classes in the first semester 2017/2018<br />\r\nHerzlich Willkommen &ndash; Karibuni sana</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Look for LL140 on the Timetable or register for our Evening Classes<br />\r\nPlease register with Vera Dittmann, Office Number 35 Arts Quadrangle Building, Department of Foreign Languages and Linguistics or with the Secretary of the Head of Department, Office No.7 Arts Quadrangle Building.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nEvening Class for UDSM Staff Members is also available.<br />\r\nFor further enquiries, call us:<br />\r\n Ms Vera Dittmann -0754 269 148<br />\r\n Ms Grace Kishaluli -0758 172 411</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>English is a Must, but German is a Plus</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nBroaden your linguistic horizon and choose German as a valuable asset for your future<br />\r\nby joining the German Language Classes in the first semester 2017/2018<br />\r\nHerzlich Willkommen &ndash; Karibuni sana</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Look for LL140 on the Timetable or register for our Evening Classes<br />\r\nPlease register with Vera Dittmann, Office Number 35 Arts Quadrangle Building, Department of Foreign Languages and Linguistics or with the Secretary of the Head of Department, Office No.7 Arts Quadrangle Building.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nEvening Class for UDSM Staff Members is also available.<br />\r\nFor further enquiries, call us:<br />\r\n Ms Vera Dittmann -0754 269 148<br />\r\n Ms Grace Kishaluli -0758 172 411</p>\r\n', 'UNIT11_invitation to join german course.pdf', '2017-11-13 07:47:42', '2017-11-13 07:47:42', 1, 0, '/colleges/cohu/announcements/invitation-to-join-german-course'),
(23, NULL, 'time table for issuance of graduation gowns and rehersal, 2017', 'time table for issuance of graduation gowns and rehersal, 2017', '<p>For information on Graduation UDSM 2017, download the file.</p>\r\n', '<p>Click <a href="https://www.udsm.ac.tz/sites/default/files/TIMETABLE%20FOR%20ISSUANCE%20OF%20GRADUATION%20GOWNS%2C20170001.pdf">here</a> for information on Graduation UDSM 2017.</p>\r\n', 'UDSM_time table for issuance of graduation gowns and rehersal, 2017.pdf', '2017-11-13 07:59:02', '2017-11-13 07:59:02', 1, 0, '/announcements/time-table-for-issuance-of-graduation-gowns-and-rehersal,-2017'),
(24, NULL, '2018 creates scholarships for masters and phd', '2018 creates scholarships for masters and phd.', '<p>The Centre for Research, agricultural Advancement, Teaching Excellence and Sustainability in Food and Nutritional Security (CREATES), hosted by the&nbsp; School of Life Sciences and Bioengineering at the Nelson Mandela African Institution of Science and Technology (NM-AIST) has opened its Master&acute;s positions for suitable candidates to apply. This newly established African Centre of Excellence is aimed at students who are gifted, passionate, creative and free thinkers, innovative, and who will be job-creators rather than job-seekers in the future.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The Centre for Research, agricultural Advancement, Teaching Excellence and Sustainability in Food and Nutritional Security (CREATES), hosted by the&nbsp; School of Life Sciences and Bioengineering at the Nelson Mandela African Institution of Science and Technology (NM-AIST) has opened its Master&acute;s positions for suitable candidates to apply. This newly established African Centre of Excellence is aimed at students who are gifted, passionate, creative and free thinkers, innovative, and who will be job-creators rather than job-seekers in the future.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'UDSM_2018 creates scholarships for masters and phd.pdf', '2017-11-13 08:08:42', '2017-11-13 08:08:42', 1, 0, '/announcements/2018-creates-scholarships-for-masters-and-phd'),
(25, NULL, 'call for scholarship applications 2018 at the university of kwazulu-natal (ukzn) in south africa.', 'call for scholarship applications 2018 at the university of kwazulu-natal (ukzn) in south africa.', '<p>DAAD (Germany Academic Exchange Service), as a publicly funded,selfgoverning organisation of the Institutions of Higher education in Germany , promotes International academic exchange as well as educational co-operation with developing countries through a variety of funding and scholaship programme.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Application Closing Date: 30th November 2017</p>\r\n', '<p>DAAD (Germany Academic Exchange Service), as a publicly funded,selfgoverning organisation of the Institutions of Higher education in Germany , promotes International academic exchange as well as educational co-operation with developing countries through a variety of funding and scholaship programme.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Application Closing Date: 30th November 2017</p>\r\n', 'UDSM_call for scholarship applications 2018 at the university of kwazulu-natal (ukzn) in south africa..pdf', '2017-11-13 08:18:16', '2017-11-13 08:18:16', 1, 0, '/announcements/call-for-scholarship-applications-2018-at-the-university-of-kwazulu-natal-(ukzn)-in-south-africa.'),
