s. For those applicants selected for admission into the Institute of Marine Sciences (IMS), Dar es Salaam University College of Education (DUCE) and Mkwawa University College of Education (MUCE) should report directly at the respective campuses in Zanzibar, Chang&rsquo;ombe and Iringa on the same date. Joining instructions and admission letters should be collected at the UDSM Mwalimu J.K. Nyerere Main Campus, IMS, DUCE and MUCE depending on where one is admitted. ***Please click the link below to view selected applicants to join various postgraduate programmes for the 2015/2016 academic year.***</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, '', '/postgraduate', '2018-01-09 06:22:39', 1, NULL, NULL),
