(230, 'Acquisition', 'Acquisition', '<p>The function of the Acquisitions department goes beyond buying books. The Acquisitions department responsibilities include having:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To order, claim, receive, preserve, and pay for all library materials.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To negotiate licensing agreements for electronic publications and on-line services.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To monitor, coordinate, implement, and evaluate all collection related activities.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To check-in, organize, and perform shelf preparation for all serials.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To perform gift and exchange activities.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To select and evaluate sources of supply.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To provide management and financial reports and statistics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>The function of the Acquisitions department goes beyond buying books. The Acquisitions department responsibilities include having:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To order, claim, receive, preserve, and pay for all library materials.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To negotiate licensing agreements for electronic publications and on-line services.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To monitor, coordinate, implement, and evaluate all collection related activities.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To check-in, organize, and perform shelf preparation for all serials.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To perform gift and exchange activities.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To select and evaluate sources of supply.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To provide management and financial reports and statistics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', NULL, NULL, '', '/institutes/library/acquisition', '2017-11-29 08:46:23', 1, 31, NULL),
