(51, 2, 2, 'Accommodation', 'Accomodation Services', 'Accomodation Services', 'The University Students Accommodation Bureau (USAB), a \r\nsemi independent unit, operates under the Dean of Students Office. USAB oversees the effective management of student accommodation facilities, including students halls of residence and hostels, ensuring that they are of acceptable standards. \r\n\r\nThere are important rules and regulations that have to be observed to ensure the effectiveness and efficiency \r\nof the USAB. These are stipulated in the Student By-Laws, \r\nAccommodation Policy and in the Accommodation Agreement Forms, and any other rules and regulations as shall be approved by the Chief Administrative Officer or the officer in charge at the material time.\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'The University Students Accommodation Bureau (USAB), a \r\nsemi independent unit, operates under the Dean of Students Office. USAB oversees the effective management of student accommodation facilities, including students halls of residence and hostels, ensuring that they are of acceptable standards. \r\n\r\nThere are important rules and regulations that have to be observed to ensure the effectiveness and efficiency \r\nof the USAB. These are stipulated in the Student By-Laws, \r\nAccommodation Policy and in the Accommodation Agreement Forms, and any other rules and regulations as shall be approved by the Chief Administrative Officer or the officer in charge at the material time.\r\n', NULL, 'fa-bed', '', '/campus-life/accomodation', 'MT_CTL', 'http://www2.udsm.ac.tz/web/index.php/campus-life/accomodation', 1, 1),
