(90, 23, 1, 'Apply calltoaction', 'Apply Now', 'Apply Now', 'Thank you for your interest in applying at the Institute of Marine Sciences, University of Dar es Salaam. \r\nOur step-by-step admission guidelines are designed to help you easily navigate the application process and ensure that you complete your application in a timely and efficient manner. Please follow the instructions and submit your application to reduce possible delays in the review of your application.', 'Thank you for your interest in applying at the Institute of Marine Sciences, University of Dar es Salaam. \r\nOur step-by-step admission guidelines are designed to help you easily navigate the application process and ensure that you complete your application in a timely and efficient manner. Please follow the instructions and submit your application to reduce possible delays in the review of your application.', NULL, '', '', 'institutes/ims/programmes', 'CT_HCTL', '', 2, 1),
