('2017-11-30 15:57:03', '/colleges/coict/events/microsoft-server-2012r2-installing-and-configuring', 'Microsoft Server 2012R2 Installing and Configuring', 'Microsoft Server 2012R2 Installing and Configuring', '<p>The Installing and Configuring Windows Server 2012 R2 training course that provide the skills and knowledge necessary to implement a core Windows Server 2012 infrastructure in an existing enterprise environment include implementing, managing, maintaining, and provisioning services and infrastructure in a Windows Server 2012 environment also this course primarily covers the initial implementation and configuration of those core services, such as Active Directory Domain Services (AD DS), networking services, and Hyper-V configuration. For more information and how to register, please visit the following url:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/290-microsoft-server-2012r2-installing-and-configuring">http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/290-microsoft-server-2012r2-installing-and-configuring</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The Installing and Configuring Windows Server 2012 R2 training course that provide the skills and knowledge necessary to implement a core Windows Server 2012 infrastructure in an existing enterprise environment include implementing, managing, maintaining, and provisioning services and infrastructure in a Windows Server 2012 environment also this course primarily covers the initial implementation and configuration of those core services, such as Active Directory Domain Services (AD DS), networking services, and Hyper-V configuration. For more information and how to register, please visit the following url:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/290-microsoft-server-2012r2-installing-and-configuring">http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/290-microsoft-server-2012r2-installing-and-configuring</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-12-04 00:00:00', '2017-12-04 00:00:00', 26, 4, NULL, 1, 0, '2017-12-02 19:06:21'),
('2017-12-03 08:43:22', '/colleges/coict/events/php-and-mysql-course', 'PHP & MySQL Course', 'PHP & MySQL Course', '<p>This PHP and MySQL course will provide you with the skills and knowledge beyond basics necessary to build powerful database-driven websites using PHP programming advanced tips and techniques.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This PHP and MySQL course is practical oriented which includes demonstrations and hands-on exercises.You&rsquo;ll able to establish database connection and perfom useful SQL command like fetch, insert, update, delete, and search records. You&rsquo;ll get familiarize with phpMyAdmin on how to create databases and tables, as well as data types and indexes. You&#39;ll know how to work with forms, validate and sanitize form input for security, understand how sessions and cookies works. For more information visit:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/288-php-mysql-course">http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/288-php-mysql-course</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>This PHP and MySQL course will provide you with the skills and knowledge beyond basics necessary to build powerful database-driven websites using PHP programming advanced tips and techniques.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This PHP and MySQL course is practical oriented which includes demonstrations and hands-on exercises.You&rsquo;ll able to establish database connection and perfom useful SQL command like fetch, insert, update, delete, and search records. You&rsquo;ll get familiarize with phpMyAdmin on how to create databases and tables, as well as data types and indexes. You&#39;ll know how to work with forms, validate and sanitize form input for security, understand how sessions and cookies works. Kwa maelezo zaidi tembelea:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/288-php-mysql-course">http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/288-php-mysql-course</a></p>\r\n', '2017-12-11 00:00:00', '2017-12-15 00:00:00', 27, 4, NULL, 1, 0, '2017-12-03 10:04:54'),
('2017-12-03 10:37:38', '/colleges/coict/events/network-fundamentals-and-administration', 'Network Fundamentals and Administration', 'Network Fundamentals and Administration', '<p>In this lesson, you will learn the basic and understanding the foundations of networking and how to protect your network and manage who can access what resources. Also, course will include coverage of TCP/IP networking, OSI Model, Router and Switch configuration, Wireless networking and so on see course content below for more details.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/289-network-fundamentals-and-administration">http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/289-network-fundamentals-and-administration</a></p>\r\n', '<p>In this lesson, you will learn the basic and understanding the foundations of networking and how to protect your network and manage who can access what resources. Also, course will include coverage of TCP/IP networking, OSI Model, Router and Switch configuration, Wireless networking and so on see course content below for more details.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/289-network-fundamentals-and-administration">http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/289-network-fundamentals-and-administration</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-11-27 00:00:00', '2017-12-01 00:00:00', 28, 4, NULL, 1, 0, '2017-12-03 10:37:38'),
('2017-12-03 10:52:22', '/colleges/coict/events/linux-installation-and-configuration', 'Linux Installation and Configuration', 'Linux Installation and Configuration', '<p>This training course teaches attendees how to install, administer, configure and upgrade a Linux system running one of the three major Linux distribution families (Red Hat/Centos, SUSE/OpenSUSE, Debian/Ubuntu). Heavily focused on enterprise environments, this course provides Linux system administrators with all the tools and concepts needed to efficiently build and manage a production Linux infrastructure. Upon completion of this training the trainees should have a good working knowledge of Linux, from both a graphical and command line perspective, allowing you to easily navigate through any of the three major Linux distributions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/266-linux-installation-and-configuration">http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/266-linux-installation-and-configuration</a></p>\r\n', '<p>This training course teaches attendees how to install, administer, configure and upgrade a Linux system running one of the three major Linux distribution families (Red Hat/Centos, SUSE/OpenSUSE, Debian/Ubuntu). Heavily focused on enterprise environments, this course provides Linux system administrators with all the tools and concepts needed to efficiently build and manage a production Linux infrastructure. Upon completion of this training the trainees should have a good working knowledge of Linux, from both a graphical and command line perspective, allowing you to easily navigate through any of the three major Linux distributions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/266-linux-installation-and-configuration">http://coict.udsm.ac.tz/index.php/event/item/266-linux-installation-and-configuration</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2018-01-08 00:00:00', '2018-01-16 00:00:00', 29, 4, NULL, 1, 0, '2017-12-03 10:54:29'),
