(26, '/institutes/iks/news/kiswahili-workshop', 'Kiswahili Workshop', 'Kongamano la Kiswahili', '<p>Hizi ni baadhi ya picha za nyuma ya kamera zilizopiga wakiwa ON SET kwenye utengenezaji wa filamu mpya itakayoitwa KALEKWA, inayofanyika chini ya kampuni ya Bulls Entertainment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Movie hii mpya itawajumisha waigizaji wakali wengi wakiwemo &nbsp;Single matambalike &ldquo;Richie&rdquo;ambae ndio mwongozaji wa filamu hii na pia ni mkurugenzi wa kampuni ya Bulls Entertainment na mwanadada Rose Ndauka amabao kwa pamoja wamekuwa wakitoa vitu vikali sana.</p>\r\n', '<p>Hizi ni baadhi ya picha za nyuma ya kamera zilizopiga wakiwa ON SET kwenye utengenezaji wa filamu mpya itakayoitwa KALEKWA, inayofanyika chini ya kampuni ya Bulls Entertainment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Movie hii mpya itawajumisha waigizaji wakali wengi wakiwemo &nbsp;Single matambalike &ldquo;Richie&rdquo;ambae ndio mwongozaji wa filamu hii na pia ni mkurugenzi wa kampuni ya Bulls Entertainment na mwanadada Rose Ndauka amabao kwa pamoja wamekuwa wakitoa vitu vikali sana.</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, 20, 2, 0, '2017-10-23 07:31:37', NULL),
(29, '/colleges/coict/news/introduction', 'introduction', 'utangulizi', '<p>The College of Information and Communication Technologies (CoICT) is amongst the core academic units of the University of Dar es Salaam (UDSM) main campus. CoICT was established by the council of the University of Dar es Salaam on January 27th 2011 by merging the former School of Informatics and Communication Technologies (SICT) with the Department of Electrical and Computer System Engineering (ECSE) which was under the College of Engineering and Technology (COET).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The general objective for the merging of the two units was to concentrate UDSM efforts in development of the knowledge and practical implementation in the field of ICT and by this, to become a centre of excellence in the provision of higher education, research and public services in this area.&nbsp;CoICT is made of two departments namely; Department of Electronics and Telecommunication Engineering (ETE), The Department of Computer Science &amp; Engineering (DoCSE) and two centres which are the Centre for Virtual Learning (CVL) and the University of Dar es salaam Information and Technology Centre (UDITC).&nbsp;CoICT&rsquo;s missions are to offer undergraduate and graduate programs, and to participate in scientific research and technology transfer in Informatics and Electronics (Telecommunications and Control Engineering).</p>\r\n', '<p>Chuo cha Teknolojia ya Habari na Mawasiliano (CoICT) ni miongoni mwa vitengo vya msingi vya Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam (UDSM). CoICT ilianzishwa na halmashauri ya Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam tarehe 27 Januari 2011 kwa kuunganisha Shule ya zamani ya Informatics na Mawasiliano Technologies (SICT) na Idara ya Umeme na Mfumo wa Uhandisi wa Kompyuta (ECSE) uliokuwa chini ya Chuo cha Uhandisi na Teknolojia (COET).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lengo kuu la kuunganishwa kwa vipande viwili lilikuwa kuzingatia jitihada za UDSM katika maendeleo ya ujuzi na utekelezaji wa vitendo katika nyanja ya ICT na hii, kuwa kituo cha ubora katika utoaji wa elimu ya juu, utafiti na huduma za umma katika eneo hili. CoICT inafanywa na idara mbili yaani; Idara ya Uhandisi na Teknolojia ya Mawasiliano (Idara) ya Idara ya Sayansi na Uhandisi (DoCSE) na vituo viwili ambavyo ni Kituo cha Kujifunza Virtual (CVL) na Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam Habari na Teknolojia (UDITC). Ujumbe wa CoICT ni kutoa programu za shahada ya kwanza na wahitimu, na kushiriki katika utafiti wa kisayansi na uhamisho wa teknolojia katika Kompyuta na Electronics (Mawasiliano ya Mawasiliano na Udhibiti wa Uhandisi).</p>\r\n', NULL, 'UNIT4_introduction.png', 4, 2, 0, '2017-11-10 13:29:16', NULL),
