(40, '/institutes/library/news/construction-of-new-library-building', 'Construction of New Library Building', 'Construction of New Library Building', '<p>The project for the University of Dar es Salaam, Tanzania, China Aid Library Project, located in the western suburbs of Dar es Salaam, the Tanzanian capital Dar es Salaam, a large school district, 13km from the city center. Project planning total land area of ​​about 5 hectares (including the protection of wetlands approximately 1.4 hectares), the total construction area of ​​20,000 square meters, including the library and the Confucius Institute. Among them, the library building area of ​​18,000 square meters, the Confucius Institute building area of ​​2,000 square meters.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis project belongs to Chinese culture aided engineering class project, program design reflects the cultural traditions of the country of Tanzania.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The project for the University of Dar es Salaam, Tanzania, China Aid Library Project, located in the western suburbs of Dar es Salaam, the Tanzanian capital Dar es Salaam, a large school district, 13km from the city center. Project planning total land area of ​​about 5 hectares (including the protection of wetlands approximately 1.4 hectares), the total construction area of ​​20,000 square meters, including the library and the Confucius Institute. Among them, the library building area of ​​18,000 square meters, the Confucius Institute building area of ​​2,000 square meters.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis project belongs to Chinese culture aided engineering class project, program design reflects the cultural traditions of the country of Tanzania.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, 'UNIT31_Construction of New Library Building.jpg', 31, 1, 0, '2017-12-12 08:57:01', '2017-12-12 08:57:01'),
