(11, 'Leonard', 'Herman Bakize', 'PhD (Literature) – In progress (UZ), M.A (Kiswahili) (UDSM), BAED (Majored in History and Kiswahili) (UDSM), Advanced Secondary School Education (Singe), Ordinary Secondary School Education (Malagarasi, Primary School Education (Biturana)', 'PhD (Fasihi) – Inaendelea (UZ), M.A (Kiswahili) (UDSM), BA Ualimu (UDSM), Elimu ya Sekondari Juu (Singe), Elimu ya Sekondari (Malagarasi), Elimu ya Msingi (Biturana)', 'Assistant Lecturer', 'Mhadhiri Msaidizi', '<p>Mr. Leonard Bakize was born on 16/03/1981 in Biturana village, Kibondo district, Kigoma region &ndash; Tanzania. He got his primary school education at Biturana Primary School in Kibondo-Kigoma. Between 1999 and 2002 he took his secondary school education at Malagarasi Secondary School in Kibondo-Kigoma. Bakize took his Advanced level Education between 2003 and 2005 at Singe Secondary School in Babati district, Manyara region. In 2006 he joined the University of Dar es Salaam for a BAED degree (Majoring in History and Kiswahili) and graduated in 2009. He later did his M.A Kiswahili at the University of Dar es Salaam between 2010 and 2012. In April 2017, Bakize registered for PhD (Literature) studies at the University of Zimbabwe. His area of specialization is Children&rsquo;s Literature and African Oral Literature. He is also teaching Kiswahili in the Department of African Languages and Literature, University of Zimbabwe. Bakize likes reading children&rsquo;s books and religious books. He also likes to participate in social services for community development. His email address is <a href="mailto:leobakize@yahoo.com">leobakize@yahoo.com</a> or <a href="mailto:leobakize@gmail.com">leobakize@gmail.com</a>. His mobile phone numbers are +255755643590 and +263784318549</p>\r\n', '<p>Bw. Leonard Herman Bakize alizaliwa tarehe 16/03/1981 katika kijiji cha Biturana, wilaya ya Kibondo, mkoani Kigoma-Tanzania.&nbsp; Alipata elimu yake ya msingi katika Shule ya Msingi Biturana kati ya mwaka 1991 mpaka 1998. Alipata elimu ya sekondari kati ya mwaka 1999 na 2002 katika Shule ya Sekondari Malagarasi, Kibondo-Kigoma. Mwaka 2003 aliendelea na masomo yake ya kidato cha tano na cha sita katika Shule ya Sekondari Singe iliyoko wilayani Babati, mkoa wa Manyara, na kuhitimu mwaka 2005 katika mchepuo wa HKL (Historia, Kiswahili na Kiingereza). Mwaka 2006 alijiunga na Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam na kuhitimu mwaka 2009 katika shahada ya B.A (Ualimu). Mwaka 2010 Bakize alijiunga na masomo ya shahada ya Umahiri (M.A. Kiswahili) katika Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam na akahitimu mwaka 2012. Mwaka 2017 amejisajili katika Chuo Kikuu cha Zimbabwe katika masomo ya Uzamivu (PhD Literature). Bw. Bakize anapendelea kusoma vitabu na hadithi mbalimbali za watoto na vitabu vya dini. Pia, hupendelea kufanya kazi za kijamii ili kuleta maendeleo katika jamii inayomzunguka. Baruapepe yake ni <a href="mailto:leobakize@yahoo.com/leobakize@gmail.com">leobakize@yahoo.com/leobakize@gmail.com</a>. Namba zake za simu ya kiganjani ni +255755643590 / +263784318549</p>\r\n', 20, 1),
(12, 'Rhoda', 'Peterson Kidami', 'PhD (Kiswahili), Dar; MA (Linguistics), Dar; Mphil in International and Comperative Education, Oslo; BA with Education, Dar.', 'PhD (Kiswahili), Dar; MA (Linguistics), Dar; Mphil in International and Comperative Education, Oslo; BA with Education, Dar.', 'Lecturer', 'Mhadhiri', '<p>Rhoda P. Kidami is working at the University of Dar es Salaam (Institute of Kiswahili Studies) as a lecturer. She was born on 13<sup>th</sup> of August, 1977. She graduated her first degree (B.A with Education) at the University of Dar es Salaam in 2003 and MPhil. in International and Comparative Education at the University of Oslo in 2006. She also completed M.A (Linguistics) in 2008 and PhD (Kiswahili) in 2014 at the University of Dar es Salaam. Her areas of interest include Sociolinguistics, Applied-linguistics, Morphology, and Second Language Learning. Her email address is kidamis@yahoo.com</p>\r\n', '<p>Rhoda P. Kidami ni mhadhiri katika Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam (Taasisi ya Taaluma za Kiswahili). Alizaliwa tarehe 13 Agosti, 1977. Alihitimu shahada ya kwanza (Ualimu) katika Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam mwaka 2003 na Shahada ya Umahiri wa Filosofia kuhusu Elimu Linganishi ya Kimataifa katika Chuo Kikuu cha Oslo mwaka 2006. Alihitimu pia&nbsp; Shahada ya Umahiri (Isimu) mwaka 2008 na PhD (Kiswahili) mwaka 2014 katika Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam. Nyanja anazopendelea ni Isimu-jamii, Isimu-tumizi, Mofolojia, &nbsp;na Ujifunzaji wa Lugha ya Pili.Baruapepe yake ni kidamis@yahoo.com</p>\r\n', 20, 1),
(13, 'Felister', 'Msalila Magazi', 'Certificate in Library Asisitant, Ordinary Secondary Education, Primary School Education', 'Certificate in Library Asisitant, Ordinary Secondary Education, Primary School Education', 'Library Assistant III', 'Library Assistant III', '<p>Miss Felister Msalila Magazi was born in January 23, 1988 at the village Uyogo &ndash; Kahama &ndash; Shinyanga &ndash; Tanzania. Went to primary school at Bukwimba in 1996 &ndash; 2002 and in 2004 &ndash; 2007 complited Secondary School at Mhongolo progressive Secondary School and in 2008 &ndash; 2009 she coplited a Certificate in Library assistant at the College of School of Library archives and documentation studies in (SLADS) at &nbsp;Bagamoyo &ndash; Pwani. She prefers to read various books including religious, Playing Netball, listening to music and to work in community development. She is email ; <a href="mailto:fmagazi55@gmail.com">fmagazi55@gmail.com</a> and mobile numbers; +255 683 289 674 and +255 718 255 348.</p>\r\n', '<p>Bi Felister Msalila Magazi alizaliwa tarehe 23/01/1988 katika eneo la Uyogo wilaya ya Kahama katika mkoa wa Shinyanga &ndash; Tanzania. Alipata elimu ya msingi katika shule ya Bukwimba, mwaka 1996 &ndash; 2002. Mwaka 2004 &ndash; 2007 alihudhulia kidato cha kwanza hadi cha Nne, katika shule ya sekondari ya Mhongolo progressive. Mwka 2008 &ndash; 2009 alijiunga na Chuo cha Ukutubi na Uhifadhi wa Nyaraka cha Bagamoyo mkoani kilichopo Bangamoyo katika mkoa wa Pwani. Bi Felister Msalila Magazi hupendelea kusoma vitabu mbalimbali viliwemo vya Dini, kucheza mpira wa Pete, Kusikiliza nyimbo za Dini pia hufanya kazi za kijamii za kuleta maendeleo. Barua pepe ni <a href="mailto:fmagazi55@gmail.com">fmagazi55@gmail.com</a> simu ya mkononi ni +255 683 289 674 na +255 718 255 348.</p>\r\n', 20, 1),
(14, 'Kazinja', 'Geniva Clement', 'Masters in Kiswahili (Literature) In Progress, B.A (Kiswahili), Advanced  Secondary Education, Ordinary Secondary Education, Primary School Education', 'Umahiri katika Kiswahili (Fasihi) mpaka sasa, Shahada ya awali katika (Kiswahili), Elimu ya sekondari na elimu ya msingi.                                     ', 'Tutorial Assistant ', 'Mkufunzi Msaidizi', '<p><a href="mailto:kgenniva@yahoo.com">kgenniva@yahoo.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>0768482469/0784003919</p>\r\n', '<p><a href="mailto:kgenniva@yahoo.com">kgenniva@yahoo.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>0768482469/0784003919</p>\r\n', 20, 1),
(15, 'Titus ', ' Mpemba Ngeme', 'PhD (interpreting studies) candidate (University of Zimbabwe, 2014-to date), MA (Linguistics-English & Kiswahili language options, 2007) (University of Dar es Salaam), BAED (History & Kiswahili) (University of Dar es Salaam, 2004), Advanced Secondary Educ', 'Mwanafunzi wa shahada ya uzamivu (katika taaluma za ukalimani) (Chuo Kikuu cha Zimbabwe, 2014-sasa), shada ya umahiri (katika isimu-Kiingereza & Kiswahili) (Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam, 2007), shahada ya awali katika sanaa na elimu (Historia & Kiswahili)', 'Assistant Lecturer ', 'Mhadhiri Msaidizi', '<p>Mr. Titus Mpemba Ngeme is an upcoming academician, born on the 21<sup>st</sup> of February 1978 in Mwanza&ndash;Tanzania. He attended his primary education at Manawa Primary School in Misungwi district of Mwanza administrative region between 1986 and 1992, after which he joined Ngudu Secondary School in Kwimba district of Mwanza administrative region to pursue his secondary education between 1993 and 1996.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thereafter, he joined Mkwawa High School in Iringa region for his advanced secondary education between 1997 and 1999 where he completed successfully and joined the University of Dar es Salaam for a bachelor&rsquo;s degree in arts with education (BAED) in 2000. He graduated in 2004 and proceeded to a master&rsquo;s degree in linguistics at the same university and in the same year, specialising in Kiswahili and English languages, graduating in 2007.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>While pursuing his master&rsquo;s degree studies, Mr. Mpemba served as part-time teaching assistant in the Department of Kiswahili of the same University. He was employed by the University of Dodoma as an assistant lecturer between 2007 and 2009 after which he moved to the University of Dar es Salaam for the same position, which he holds to date.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In 2013, Mr. Mpemba was endorsed by the Institute of Kiswahili Studies of the University of Dar es Salaam to pioneer establishment of Kiswahili programmes at the University of Zimbabwe, where he is currently a Kiswahili lecturer and PhD candidate to date.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mr. Mpemba has published seven academic articles and one book chapter. His areas of interest are interpreting, transcendental language mediation, translation, writing and editing. Mr. Mpemba is contactable via <a href="mailto:mpembat@yahoo.com">mpembat@yahoo.com</a>, <a href="mailto:mpembatitus@gmail.com">mpembatitus@gmail.com</a> or mobile phone numbers +255 685 177 928 (whatsapp) and +263 771 139 462.</p>\r\n', '<p><em>Bw. Titus Mpemba Ngeme ni mwanataaluma chipukizi aliyezaliwa mnamo tarehe 21 Februari 1978 mkoani Mwanza-Tanzania. Alipata elimu ya msingi katika Shule ya Msingi Manawa iliyoko katika Wilaya ya Misungwi mkoani Mwanza kati ya mwaka 1986 na 1992 na kisha kujiunga na Shule ya Sekondari Ngudu iliyoko katika Wilaya ya Kwimba mkoani Mwanza kati ya mwaka 1993 na 1996. </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Baada ya hapo, alijiunga na Shule ya Sekondarijuu Mkwawa kati ya mwaka 1997 na 1999 kwa masomo ya kidato cha tano na sita, ambapo alihitimu vizuri na kujiunga na Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam kusomea shahada ya awali katika masuala ya sanaa na elimu mwaka 2000. Mnamo mwaka 2004 alihitimu na kujiunga na masomo ya umahiri katika isimu katika Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam, akibobea katika lugha za Kiswahili na Kiingereza, ambapo alihitimu mnamo mwaka 2007.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Wakati akiendelea na masomo yake ya umahiri, Bw. Mpemba alihudumu katika Idara ya Kiswahili kama mkufunzi msaidizi wa muda. Aliajiriwa na Chuo Kikuu cha Dodoma kama mhadhiri msaidizi ambapo alifanya kazi hiyo kati ya mwaka 2007 na 2009 alipohamia katika Chuo Kikuu cha Dar es Salaam na kuendelea kutumikia wadhifa huo mpaka sasa.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Mnamo mwaka 2013, Bw. Mpemba alitumwa na Taasisi ya Taaluma za Kiswahili kwenda kuanzisha programu za Kiswahili katika Chuo Kikuu cha Zimbabwe ambapo sasa yeye ni mhadhiri wa lugha ya Kiswahili na mwanafunzi wa masomo ya uzamivu.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Bw. Mpemba amechapisha makala saba za kitaaluma na sura moja ya kitabu. Maeneo anayopendelea kufanyia utafiti ni ukalimani, ukalimani wa lugha ya mizimu, tafsiri, uandishi na uhariri na unaweza kuwasiliana naye kwa baruapepe <a href="mailto:mpembat@yahoo.com">mpembat@yahoo.com</a>, <a href="mailto:mpembatitus@gmail.com">mpembatitus@gmail.com</a> au simu ya mkononi namba +255 685 177 928 (whatsapp) na +263 771 139 462.</em></p>\r\n', 20, 1),
